<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
<title>Laguna Diving Experience</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,700&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
:root{--deep:#050d1a;--coral:#ff6b4a;--coral-glow:#ff8a6e;--gold:#ffc857;--gold-dim:#b8943f;--sand:#ffecd2;--cyan:#4ecdc4;--white:#fff}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;background:var(--deep);color:var(--white);min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
.ocean-bg{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#050d1a 0%,#0b1a30 25%,#0e2240 50%,#12304f 75%,#1a4670 100%)}
.ocean-bg::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 150% 50% at 20% 80%,rgba(78,205,196,0.06) 0%,transparent 60%),radial-gradient(ellipse 100% 60% at 80% 20%,rgba(255,107,74,0.04) 0%,transparent 50%)}
.waves{position:fixed;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:120px;z-index:1;pointer-events:none;overflow:hidden}
.wave{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:200%;height:100%;animation:waveFlow linear infinite}
.wave1{background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent 0%,rgba(78,205,196,0.03) 25%,rgba(78,205,196,0.06) 50%,rgba(78,205,196,0.03) 75%,transparent 100%);background-size:50% 100%;animation-duration:18s;height:60px}
.wave2{background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent 0%,rgba(255,107,74,0.02) 25%,rgba(255,107,74,0.05) 50%,rgba(255,107,74,0.02) 75%,transparent 100%);background-size:50% 100%;animation-duration:14s;animation-direction:reverse;bottom:20px;height:50px}
@keyframes waveFlow{from{transform:translateX(0)}to{transform:translateX(-50%)}}
.bubbles{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:1;pointer-events:none;overflow:hidden}
.bubble{position:absolute;bottom:-30px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%,rgba(255,255,255,0.12),rgba(255,255,255,0.01));border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);animation:rise linear infinite}
@keyframes rise{0%{transform:translateY(0) translateX(0) scale(1);opacity:0.5}40%{opacity:0.3}100%{transform:translateY(-110vh) translateX(30px) scale(0.6);opacity:0}}
.particles{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:1;pointer-events:none}
.particle{position:absolute;width:3px;height:3px;background:rgba(255,200,87,0.3);border-radius:50%;animation:drift 20s linear infinite}
@keyframes drift{0%{transform:translate(0,0) scale(1);opacity:0}10%{opacity:0.6}90%{opacity:0.6}100%{transform:translate(100px,-200px) scale(0);opacity:0}}
.container{position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:540px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px 18px 80px;min-height:100vh}
.header{text-align:center;padding:28px 0 16px;animation:fadeDown 0.8s ease-out}
@keyframes fadeDown{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-20px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
.logo{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:10px}
.logo-icon{width:52px;height:52px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--coral),#e05535);border-radius:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:26px;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(255,107,74,0.35);animation:logoPulse 3s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes logoPulse{0%,100%{box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(255,107,74,0.35)}50%{box-shadow:0 4px 32px rgba(255,107,74,0.5)}}
.logo-text{font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:24px;color:var(--sand)}
.logo-sub{font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:4px;color:var(--coral-glow);font-weight:500}
.sound-toggle{position:fixed;top:18px;right:18px;z-index:100;width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(10px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:20px;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.3s;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent}
.sound-toggle:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1)}
.sound-toggle.active{background:rgba(255,107,74,0.15);border-color:rgba(255,107,74,0.3)}
.progress-wrap{margin:0 0 28px}
.progress-info{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:6px}
.progress-bar{height:3px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.progress-fill{height:100%;border-radius:4px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--coral),var(--gold));transition:width 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);box-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(255,107,74,0.3)}
.card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);backdrop-filter:blur(24px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(24px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:22px;padding:30px 26px;margin-bottom:16px;animation:cardIn 0.5s ease-out;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(255,255,255,0.1),transparent)}
@keyframes cardIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px) scale(0.97)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0) scale(1)}}
.q-num{font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:4px;color:var(--coral);margin-bottom:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.q-num::after{content:'';flex:1;height:1px;background:rgba(255,107,74,0.12)}
.q-text{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:600;line-height:1.3;color:var(--sand);margin-bottom:6px}
.q-hint{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.25);margin-bottom:22px;font-style:italic;line-height:1.5}
.q-photo{width:100%;max-width:280px;margin:0 auto 14px;display:block;border-radius:16px;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);box-shadow:0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4)}
.photo-cap{text-align:center;font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);font-style:italic;margin:-6px 0 18px}
.options{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:9px}
.option{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:14px;padding:15px 18px;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.25s ease;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:13px;font-size:14.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);line-height:1.4;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent}
.option:hover{background:rgba(255,107,74,0.04);border-color:rgba(255,107,74,0.2);transform:translateX(4px)}
.option.selected{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,107,74,0.1),rgba(255,200,87,0.05));border-color:var(--coral);color:var(--white);box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(255,107,74,0.08)}
.o-dot{width:22px;height:22px;min-width:22px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all 0.25s}
.option.selected .o-dot{border-color:var(--coral);background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--coral),#e05535);box-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(255,107,74,0.3)}
.option.selected .o-dot::after{content:'\2713';font-size:11px;color:white;font-weight:700}
.o-emoji{font-size:20px;min-width:26px;text-align:center}
.nav-buttons{display:flex;gap:10px;margin-top:8px}
.btn{flex:1;padding:16px 22px;border-radius:14px;font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:14.5px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.25s;border:none;letter-spacing:0.3px}
.btn-back{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);flex:0.35}
.btn-back:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6)}
.btn-next{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--coral),#d44a2e);color:white;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(255,107,74,0.3)}
.btn-next:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(255,107,74,0.4)}
.btn-next:disabled{opacity:0.2;cursor:not-allowed;transform:none;box-shadow:none}
.intro-screen{text-align:center;padding:10px 0}
.intro-hero{font-size:80px;margin-bottom:24px;display:block;animation:heroFloat 4s ease-in-out infinite;filter:drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(255,107,74,0.2))}
@keyframes heroFloat{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0) rotate(0deg)}25%{transform:translateY(-8px) rotate(2deg)}75%{transform:translateY(-4px) rotate(-2deg)}}
.intro-screen h2{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:30px;font-weight:600;color:var(--sand);margin-bottom:14px;line-height:1.2}
.intro-screen h2 em{color:var(--coral);font-style:italic;text-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(255,107,74,0.2)}
.intro-screen p{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);font-size:14.5px;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px;max-width:420px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto}
.intro-box{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,107,74,0.06),rgba(255,200,87,0.03));border:1px solid rgba(255,107,74,0.1);border-radius:16px;padding:18px 22px;margin:24px 0;font-size:13.5px;color:var(--coral-glow);line-height:1.6}
.start-btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--coral),#d44a2e);color:white;border:none;padding:18px 50px;border-radius:60px;font-family:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.3s;box-shadow:0 6px 30px rgba(255,107,74,0.35);letter-spacing:0.3px;margin-top:20px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;animation:btnGlow 3s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes btnGlow{0%,100%{box-shadow:0 6px 30px rgba(255,107,74,0.35)}50%{box-shadow:0 6px 40px rgba(255,107,74,0.5)}}
.start-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-3px) scale(1.02)}

/* INTERSTITIAL STYLES */
.interstitial{text-align:center;animation:cardIn 0.5s ease-out}
.inter-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);backdrop-filter:blur(24px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(24px);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:22px;padding:30px 24px;margin-bottom:16px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.inter-card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(255,200,87,0.15),transparent)}
.inter-quote{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;color:var(--sand);line-height:1.4;margin:16px 0}
.inter-author{font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.25);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:16px}
.inter-photo{width:100%;max-width:300px;margin:16px auto;display:block;border-radius:16px;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);box-shadow:0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4)}
.inter-cap{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.18);font-style:italic;margin-top:6px}
.inter-tag{display:inline-block;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,200,87,0.1),rgba(255,107,74,0.05));border:1px solid rgba(255,200,87,0.15);border-radius:20px;padding:6px 16px;font-size:11px;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;margin-bottom:14px}

/* SCRATCH CARD */
.scratch-wrap{position:relative;width:280px;height:280px;margin:16px auto;border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);box-shadow:0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4)}
.scratch-img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block}
.scratch-canvas{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;cursor:pointer;touch-action:none;border-radius:16px}
.scratch-hint{font-size:13px;color:var(--gold);margin-top:10px;animation:pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:0.6}50%{opacity:1}}
.scratch-revealed{font-size:15px;color:var(--coral-glow);margin-top:10px;animation:cardIn 0.5s ease-out}

/* RESULT */
.result-screen{text-align:center;padding:10px 0}
.result-badge{width:100px;height:100px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--coral),var(--gold));display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:48px;margin:0 auto 24px;box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(255,107,74,0.3);animation:badgePop 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.175,0.885,0.32,1.275)}
@keyframes badgePop{from{transform:scale(0) rotate(-20deg)}to{transform:scale(1) rotate(0)}}
.result-screen h2{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:30px;font-weight:600;color:var(--sand);margin-bottom:10px}
.result-screen .subtitle{color:var(--coral-glow);font-size:15px;margin-bottom:24px;font-style:italic}
.r-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:18px;padding:24px;margin:16px 0;text-align:left}
.r-card h3{font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:14px;color:var(--coral);margin-bottom:14px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2.5px}
.r-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03);font-size:13.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);line-height:1.5}
.r-item:last-child{border:none}
.r-icon{min-width:24px;height:24px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,107,74,0.12),rgba(255,200,87,0.06));border-radius:7px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:12px;margin-top:1px}
.r-note{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,200,87,0.06),rgba(255,107,74,0.03));border:1px solid rgba(255,200,87,0.1);border-radius:16px;padding:20px 24px;margin:20px 0;font-size:14.5px;color:var(--gold);line-height:1.6;text-align:center}
.stat{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);border-radius:14px;padding:14px 18px;margin:8px 0;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03)}
.stat-icon{font-size:24px}.stat-label{font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px}.stat-val{font-size:15px;color:var(--sand);font-weight:500}
.r-photo{width:100%;max-width:320px;margin:20px auto;display:block;border-radius:18px;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);box-shadow:0 12px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.4)}
.footer{text-align:center;padding:30px 0 16px;font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);line-height:1.6}
.hidden{display:none!important}
.shimmer{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--sand) 0%,var(--gold) 50%,var(--sand) 100%);background-size:200%;-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;animation:shimmer 3s linear infinite}
@keyframes shimmer{from{background-position:200%}to{background-position:-200%}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="ocean-bg"></div>
<div class="waves"><div class="wave wave1"></div><div class="wave wave2"></div></div>
<div class="bubbles" id="bubbles"></div>
<div class="particles" id="particles"></div>
<div class="sound-toggle" id="soundBtn" onclick="toggleSound()">üîá</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header">

      <div class="logo-icon">ü§ø</div>
      <div><div class="logo-text">Laguna Diving</div><div class="logo-sub">Experience ¬∑ Venezia</div></div>

    <span class="intro-hero">üêô</span>

    <p>Prima di immergerti nelle acque segrete della laguna veneta, il nostro team ha bisogno di conoscerti. A fondo.</p>
    <p>Il questionario √® obbligatorio, semiserio, e decisamente invadente.</p>
    <div class="intro-box">üéÇ <strong>Pacchetto Birthday Edition attivato.</strong><br>Il tuo accompagnatore ha richiesto il trattamento speciale.<br>Non fare domande. Non opporre resistenza. Non cercare su Google.</div>
    <button class="start-btn" onclick="startQuiz()">Inizia il Questionario ‚Üí</button>

      <button class="btn btn-back" id="btnBack" onclick="prev()">‚Üê Indietro</button>

    </div>

</div>
<script>
const bEl=document.getElementById('bubbles');for(let i=0;i<22;i++){const b=document.createElement('div');b.className='bubble';const s=Math.random()*22+4;b.style.cssText=`width:${s}px;height:${s}px;left:${Math.random()*100}%;animation-duration:${Math.random()*12+8}s;animation-delay:${Math.random()*10}s`;bEl.appendChild(b)}
const pEl=document.getElementById('particles');for(let i=0;i<15;i++){const p=document.createElement('div');p.className='particle';p.style.cssText=`left:${Math.random()*100}%;top:${Math.random()*100}%;animation-delay:${Math.random()*20}s;animation-duration:${Math.random()*15+10}s`;pEl.appendChild(p)}
let audioCtx=null,isPlaying=false;
function toggleSound(){const btn=document.getElementById('soundBtn');if(!audioCtx){audioCtx=new(window.AudioContext||window.webkitAudioContext)();const bufSize=2*audioCtx.sampleRate;const buf=audioCtx.createBuffer(2,bufSize,audioCtx.sampleRate);for(let ch=0;ch<2;ch++){const d=buf.getChannelData(ch);let last=0;for(let i=0;i<bufSize;i++){const w=Math.random()*2-1;d[i]=(last+0.02*w)/1.02;last=d[i];d[i]*=2.5}}const src=audioCtx.createBufferSource();src.buffer=buf;src.loop=true;const gain=audioCtx.createGain();gain.gain.value=0.12;const lp=audioCtx.createBiquadFilter();lp.type='lowpass';lp.frequency.value=400;src.connect(lp);lp.connect(gain);gain.connect(audioCtx.destination);src.start();const lfo=audioCtx.createOscillator();lfo.frequency.value=0.1;const lfoGain=audioCtx.createGain();lfoGain.gain.value=80;lfo.connect(lfoGain);lfoGain.connect(lp.frequency);lfo.start()}if(isPlaying){audioCtx.suspend();btn.textContent='\ud83d\udd07';btn.classList.remove('active')}else{audioCtx.resume();btn.textContent='\ud83d\udd0a';btn.classList.add('active')}isPlaying=!isPlaying}
const IMG={
  mountain_face:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  couple_mountain:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  with_dog:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  spa_sunglasses:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  pool_float:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  couple_window:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  selfie_hills:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  couple_heart:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  museum_stripes:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  couple_retro:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  couple_river:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  mermaid_bar:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  dog_forest:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  couple_lobster:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  her_gallery:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  her_rocks_water:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  her_neon_bar:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  couple_halloween:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
  couple_peru:"data:image/jpeg;base64,",
};


const STEPS=[
  // Q1
  {type:"q",n:1,t:"Quanto riesci a trattenere il fiato?",h:"Sii onesta. Il polpo istruttore legge le risposte in diretta.",img:"mountain_face",cap:"Foto d\u2019archivio: la candidata in apnea emotiva ad alta quota",opts:[
    {e:"\ud83d\ude24",t:"Abbastanza da sembrare morta e poi rinascere drammaticamente"},
    {e:"\ud83d\ude2e\u200d\ud83d\udca8",t:"Il tempo di un\u2019apnea in vasca da bagno. Forse."},
    {e:"\ud83d\ude31",t:"Mi dimentico di respirare solo guardando serie TV"},
    {e:"\ud83d\udc80",t:"Gi\u00e0 respiro a malapena normalmente, figurati sott\u2019acqua"}]},
  // Q2
  {type:"q",n:2,t:"Qual \u00e8 il tuo rapporto con i pesci?",h:"La fauna marina ha chiesto referenze su di te.",opts:[
    {e:"\ud83d\udc20",t:"Li trovo adorabili, ci parlerei per ore"},
    {e:"\ud83c\udf63",t:"Li preferisco crudi, con salsa di soia e wasabi"},
    {e:"\ud83d\ude28",t:"Se mi guardano negli occhi, perdo il controllo"},
    {e:"\ud83e\udddc\u200d\u2640\ufe0f",t:"In una vita precedente ero una sirena e lo confermo"}]},
  // Q3
  {type:"q",n:3,t:"Come reagisci quando ti si bagnano i capelli senza preavviso?",h:"Determinante per l\u2019assegnazione della zona d\u2019immersione.",opts:[

let cur=0,ans={},qCount=0,scratchDone={};
const totalQ=STEPS.filter(s=>s.type==="q").length;

function startQuiz(){
  document.getElementById('intro').classList.add('hidden');
  document.getElementById('quiz').classList.remove('hidden');
  render();
}

function getQNum(){
  let c=0;
  for(let i=0;i<=cur;i++)if(STEPS[i].type==="q")c++;
  return c;
}

function render(){
  const step=STEPS[cur];
  const c=document.getElementById('qcontainer');
  const qn=getQNum();
  const pct=Math.round((qn/totalQ)*100);
  document.getElementById('plabel').textContent=`Domanda ${qn} di ${totalQ}`;
  document.getElementById('ppct').textContent=pct+'%';
  document.getElementById('pfill').style.width=pct+'%';
  document.getElementById('btnBack').style.display=cur===0?'none':'block';

  if(step.type==="q"){
    let ph='';
    if(step.img)ph=`<img src="${IMG[step.img]}" class="q-photo" alt=""><div class="photo-cap">${step.cap||''}</div>`;
    c.innerHTML=`<div class="card"><div class="q-num">Domanda ${step.n}</div><div class="q-text">${step.t}</div><div class="q-hint">${step.h}</div>${ph}<div class="options">${step.opts.map((o,i)=>`<div class="option ${ans[cur]===i?'selected':''}" onclick="sel(${i})"><span class="o-dot"></span><span class="o-emoji">${o.e}</span><span>${o.t}</span></div>`).join('')}</div></div>`;
    document.getElementById('btnNext').disabled=ans[cur]===undefined;
    document.getElementById('btnNext').textContent=cur===STEPS.length-1?'Scopri il Risultato \u2728':'Avanti \u2192';
  }
  else if(step.type==="inter"){
    c.innerHTML=`<div class="interstitial"><div class="inter-card"><div class="inter-tag">${step.tag}</div><div class="inter-quote">${step.quote}</div><div class="inter-author">\u2014 ${step.author}</div><img src="${IMG[step.img]}" class="inter-photo" alt=""><div class="inter-cap">${step.cap}</div></div></div>`;
    document.getElementById('btnNext').disabled=false;
    document.getElementById('btnNext').textContent='Avanti \u2192';
    ans[cur]='seen';
  }
  else if(step.type==="scratch"){
    const done=scratchDone[cur];
    c.innerHTML=`<div class="interstitial"><div class="inter-card"><div class="inter-tag">${step.tag}</div><div class="q-text" style="margin-bottom:12px">${step.title}</div>${done?`<img src="${IMG[step.img]}" class="inter-photo" alt="" style="max-width:280px"><div class="scratch-revealed">${step.revealText}</div>`:`<div class="scratch-wrap"><img src="${IMG[step.img]}" class="scratch-img" alt=""><canvas class="scratch-canvas" id="scratchCanvas"></canvas></div><div class="scratch-hint">\ud83d\udc46 ${step.hint}</div>`}</div></div>`;
    if(!done)initScratch(cur);
    document.getElementById('btnNext').disabled=!done;
    document.getElementById('btnNext').textContent='Avanti \u2192';
    if(done)ans[cur]='scratched';
  }
}

function initScratch(stepIdx){
  const canvas=document.getElementById('scratchCanvas');
  if(!canvas)return;
  const rect=canvas.parentElement.getBoundingClientRect();
  canvas.width=rect.width;canvas.height=rect.height;
  const ctx=canvas.getContext('2d');
  // Draw scratch overlay
  ctx.fillStyle='#1a3a5c';ctx.fillRect(0,0,canvas.width,canvas.height);
  ctx.fillStyle='rgba(255,200,87,0.15)';
  ctx.font='bold 16px Space Grotesk';ctx.textAlign='center';
  ctx.fillText('GRATTA QUI! \ud83d\udc46',canvas.width/2,canvas.height/2-10);
  ctx.font='12px Space Grotesk';ctx.fillStyle='rgba(255,255,255,0.2)';
  ctx.fillText('Usa il dito per scoprire',canvas.width/2,canvas.height/2+20);
  // Draw some decorative circles
  for(let i=0;i<20;i++){ctx.beginPath();ctx.arc(Math.random()*canvas.width,Math.random()*canvas.height,Math.random()*15+5,0,Math.PI*2);ctx.fillStyle=`rgba(255,107,74,${Math.random()*0.08})`;ctx.fill()}
  let isDrawing=false,totalScratched=0;
  const totalPixels=canvas.width*canvas.height;
  function scratch(x,y){
    ctx.globalCompositeOperation='destination-out';
    ctx.beginPath();ctx.arc(x,y,28,0,Math.PI*2);ctx.fill();
    totalScratched+=28*28*Math.PI;
    if(totalScratched>totalPixels*0.35){scratchDone[stepIdx]=true;document.getElementById('btnNext').disabled=false;render()}
  }
  function getPos(e){
    const r=canvas.getBoundingClientRect();
    const t=e.touches?e.touches[0]:e;
    return{x:t.clientX-r.left,y:t.clientY-r.top}
  }
  canvas.addEventListener('mousedown',e=>{isDrawing=true;const p=getPos(e);scratch(p.x,p.y)});
  canvas.addEventListener('mousemove',e=>{if(isDrawing){const p=getPos(e);scratch(p.x,p.y)}});
  canvas.addEventListener('mouseup',()=>isDrawing=false);
  canvas.addEventListener('touchstart',e=>{e.preventDefault();isDrawing=true;const p=getPos(e);scratch(p.x,p.y)},{passive:false});
  canvas.addEventListener('touchmove',e=>{e.preventDefault();if(isDrawing){const p=getPos(e);scratch(p.x,p.y)}},{passive:false});
  canvas.addEventListener('touchend',()=>isDrawing=false);
}

function sel(i){ans[cur]=i;document.querySelectorAll('.option').forEach((el,idx)=>el.classList.toggle('selected',idx===i));document.getElementById('btnNext').disabled=false}

function next(){
  if(ans[cur]===undefined)return;
  if(cur<STEPS.length-1){cur++;render();window.scrollTo({top:0,behavior:'smooth'})}
  else{showResult();window.scrollTo({top:0,behavior:'smooth'})}
}
function prev(){if(cur>0){cur--;render()}}

function getAns(qNum){
  for(let i=0;i<STEPS.length;i++){if(STEPS[i].type==="q"&&STEPS[i].n===qNum)return ans[i]}
  return 0;
}

function showResult(){
  document.getElementById('quiz').classList.add('hidden');
  const r=document.getElementById('result');r.classList.remove('hidden');
  const mAns=getAns(11)||0;
  let mText="Sveglia: decider\u00e0 il capitano";
  if(mAns===0)mText="Colazione lenta garantita. Silenzio sacro rispettato.";
  if(mAns===1)mText="Alba confermata. Sveglia presto per te.";
  if(mAns===2)mText="Check-out posticipato. Nessuno ti disturber\u00e0 prima delle 10.";
  if(mAns===3)mText="40 minuti di scroll concessi. Poi si parte.";
  const pAns=getAns(14)||0;
  const animals=["Leone Spaesato \ud83e\udd81","Orso Affamato \ud83d\udc3b","Volpe Misteriosa \ud83e\udd8a","Polpo Stratega \ud83d\udc19"];
  r.innerHTML=`<div class="result-screen"><div class="result-badge">\ud83c\udf89</div><h2 class="shimmer">Idoneit\u00e0 Confermata!</h2><p class="subtitle">Sei ufficialmente arruolata nell\u2019equipaggio</p><img src="${IMG.spa_sunglasses}" class="r-photo" alt=""><p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.18);font-size:11px;font-style:italic;margin:-10px 0 20px">La recluta nel suo habitat naturale</p><div class="stat"><span class="stat-icon">\ud83e\udec1</span><div><div class="stat-label">Capacit\u00e0 polmonare</div><div class="stat-val">Sufficiente per sopravvivere (forse)</div></div></div><div class="stat"><span class="stat-icon">\ud83d\udc20</span><div><div class="stat-label">Compatibilit\u00e0 fauna marina</div><div class="stat-val">74% \u2014 i polpi restano perplessi</div></div></div><div class="stat"><span class="stat-icon">\ud83d\udc85</span><div><div class="stat-label">Eleganza subacquea</div><div class="stat-val">Fuori scala. La muta non \u00e8 necessaria.</div></div></div><div class="stat"><span class="stat-icon">\ud83e\udd81</span><div><div class="stat-label">Accompagnatore classificato come</div><div class="stat-val">${animals[pAns]}</div></div></div><div class="stat"><span class="stat-icon">\u2728</span><div><div class="stat-label">Prontezza emotiva</div><div class="stat-val">Pronta per qualcosa di indimenticabile</div></div></div><div class="r-card"><h3>\ud83d\udccd Briefing Missione</h3><div class="r-item"><span class="r-icon">\ud83d\udcc5</span><span>Quando: weekend del tuo compleanno</span></div><div class="r-item"><span class="r-icon">\ud83c\udf0a</span><span>Dove: laguna veneta \u2014 coordinate classificate</span></div><div class="r-item"><span class="r-icon">\u23f0</span><span>${mText}</span></div><div class="r-item"><span class="r-icon">\ud83d\udd52</span><span>Durata: 2 giorni / 1 notte di immersione totale</span></div><div class="r-item"><span class="r-icon">\ud83e\udd2b</span><span>Livello segretezza: MASSIMO. Non indagare.</span></div></div><div class="r-note">\ud83c\udf82 <strong>Messaggio dal capitano:</strong><br><br>Tutto \u00e8 stato pensato con cura.<br>L\u2019unica cosa che devi fare \u00e8 fidarti e goderti il viaggio.<br><br>Buon compleanno. \u2764\ufe0f</div><img src="${IMG.couple_peru}" class="r-photo" alt="" style="margin-top:24px"><p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);font-size:11px;font-style:italic;margin:6px 0 0">Il capitano e la sua ciurma preferita</p><p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);font-size:10px;margin-top:32px;line-height:1.7">Disclaimer: Laguna Diving Experience non \u00e8 responsabile per emozioni improvvise, lacrime senza motivo, farfalle allo stomaco, battiti cardiaci irregolari, o ricordi che porterai con te per il resto della vita. Procedere a proprio rischio emotivo.</p></div>`;
}
</script></body></html>
